config.text:
Welcome to the Millcreek Map Explorer.

Please use the buttons to the to explore maps and data specific to Millcreek, UT.


  • Planning and Zoning

Land use information, current projects, zoning, and aerial photos.


  • General Information

Boundaries, utilities, and political representation.


  • Sensitive Lands

Faults, fault study zones, liquefication potential, slopes, and overlay zones.


  • Transportation

Centerlines, functional classes, active transportation, UTA bus information.


  • Hydrology & Storm Drain

Hydrology, floodplains, storm drain infrastructure, watersheds, and irrigation canals.


  • Promise Program

School information, social and digital equity, community assets, safe routes and little libraries.


  • Electronic Documents

Access electronic documents from the Salt Lake County Assessor's office.
